This final workshop explores various topics, including the inference of population structure using pool-seq data, the gennome scanning for markers exhibiting excess of differentiation (Fst or XtX), as well as genotype-environment associations (Bayes Factors). The practical also explains how to perform neutral calibrations of these metrics through simulations.

Main instructor: Thibault Leroy (thibault.leroy_at_inrae.fr)
